title: The Nightly Duo
body_html:
The Nightly Duo, the perfect combination of Flawless Nightly 2% Retinoid Serum and Flawless Nightly Eye 2% Retinoid Serum. This gentle active serum duo contains Granactive Retinoid®, Niacinamide, Azelaic Acid and Bakuchiol, to soften lines and give skin a grown-up glow with just one layer of the serum.

The eye serum helps reduce fine lines, brighten dark circles, and nourish dehydrated skin with vitamin C. Together, these two serums give skin a complete solution to look refreshed and rejuvenated.
